data.text:
Welcome to Capital Health Primary Care – Mountain View

We are pleased that you have chosen us as your primary care specialists. Capital Health Primary Care - Mountain View is led by Dr. Katherina Canales, Dr. Scott Kolander, Dr. Shaismy Kudakachira, Dr. Benjamin Sussman, and Dr. Clare Gosek. The team of skilled, board certified physicians at Capital Health Primary Care - Mountain View offers preventive medicine, geriatric care, minor surgery, access to the area's finest specialists, virtually everything necessary to meet your primary medical needs.

Our practice offers appointment hours for check-ups, follow-up visits, and when you're not feeling well. Our goal is to offer you and your family the highest quality medical care. We will strive to meet this goal and look forward to seeing you at your next visit.
